# Mobile/Network Access Configuration
# 
# To access the app on your phone or other devices on the same network:
# 1. Find your computer's IP address (e.g., 192.168.1.x)
# 2. Create a .env file in the frontend directory with:
#    VITE_API_URL=http://YOUR_IP_ADDRESS:9204
#
# On Mac: System Preferences > Network > Wi-Fi > Advanced > TCP/IP
# On Windows: ipconfig > IPv4 Address
